  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'

import { Label } from './index';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`//import '../styles/scss/theme.scss';
//import t from '../i18n';
const t = ()=> "";`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"entry-label"}}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="h1">{`Entry Label`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>

<PropsTable of={Label} />

<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"exemplos"}}>{`Exemplos`}</MDXTag>
